    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > </h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063780/extras/2686895852d9bce5fbd8216e0fc8c4dc.avif?t=1751451756\" width=616 height=346 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这是一款<strong>经典的捉鬼</strong>游戏，充满了<strong>谜题、突如其来的惊吓和有趣的合作追逐 </strong>。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>👻 和朋友捉恶魔，边笑边逃命</strong>  <br>融合<strong>惊悚追逐</strong>、<strong>合作解谜</strong>与<strong>探索</strong>的恐怖体验。赶紧开始你的心跳体验！</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>3张超大地图</strong>：古宅、学校、工厂下水道，够你玩到爽！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>2种模式任选</strong>：<strong>经典模式</strong>新手友好，<strong>疯狂模式</strong>解锁10种恐怖能力恶魔！</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063780/extras/1d6e5d1840fc8e53f0de40baf2ef555f.poster.avif?t=1751451756\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063780/extras/1d6e5d1840fc8e53f0de40baf2ef555f.webm?t=1751451756\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063780/extras/1d6e5d1840fc8e53f0de40baf2ef555f.mp4?t=1751451756\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>👻 玩法超简单，上手就尖叫！</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>找到鬼房</strong>：使用<strong>十字架</strong>、<strong>米迦勒之心</strong>、<strong>圣水</strong>等圣器，找到恶魔的痕迹（如幽灵的怪叫、漂浮空中的物品）。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>道具随便玩</strong>：带上头灯，拿上道具。快点找出恶魔的身影！圣水泼鬼会露出身影，花束见鬼会立刻凋谢，心脏会结冰。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>抓住恶魔</strong>：找到对的道具（圣器），立刻到台子（祭坛）封印恶魔吧！</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>用增强道具逃生</strong>：躲进衣柜、用变声器和队友语音学唐老鸭说话，吃药丸变成恶魔的样子恶搞、摇响铃铛帮助你的队友复活，别让恶魔抓到你！</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063780/extras/5c0affe1dcc8b813e4d6855eb58a54e3.poster.avif?t=1751451756\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063780/extras/5c0affe1dcc8b813e4d6855eb58a54e3.webm?t=1751451756\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063780/extras/5c0affe1dcc8b813e4d6855eb58a54e3.mp4?t=1751451756\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>👻 精彩的追逐系统</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >若你追求《<strong>恐鬼症</strong>》的惊悚、《<strong>致命公司</strong>》《<strong>动物公司</strong>》的有趣追逐，或《<strong>玩具熊的五夜后宫</strong>》的氛围环境，这将是你的噩梦新开始。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>疯狂模式</strong>开启时，恶魔拥有特殊能力：专杀落单者！<strong>快逃</strong>！与队友汇合，否则将成为恶魔的猎物。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>👻 策略性增强道具</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >想要玩点有趣的？使用<strong>加速棒棒糖</strong>摆脱追杀，吞下<strong>拟态药丸</strong>伪装成恶魔制造混乱。你甚至可以对着手柄<strong>吹燃鼠尾草</strong>让恶魔退散！更多增强道具等你探索。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063780/extras/3290244f10a84f90c88a0b603eb4ad57.poster.avif?t=1751451756\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063780/extras/3290244f10a84f90c88a0b603eb4ad57.webm?t=1751451756\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063780/extras/3290244f10a84f90c88a0b603eb4ad57.mp4?t=1751451756\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>👻 自定义你的形象</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >有创造力一些吧！解锁<strong>独特Avatar</strong>与<strong>神秘面具</strong>，成为最耀眼的驱魔专家。如果你喜爱《<strong>Gorilla Tag</strong>》《<strong>Yeeps</strong>》平台游戏的高自由度装扮，这里将继续满足你的创意——打造专属你的形象！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你会拥有FNAF中的freddy熊面具、带翅膀的天使阿凡达....</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063780/extras/66263d67ebfdbaa91467a6aec395b680.poster.avif?t=1751451756\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063780/extras/66263d67ebfdbaa91467a6aec395b680.webm?t=1751451756\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063780/extras/66263d67ebfdbaa91467a6aec395b680.mp4?t=1751451756\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>核心特色</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >单人/合作模式（最多3人）</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >多交互（沙盒式）探索</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >多样化每日/每周任务</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与恶魔的追逐逃跑</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
